# Basic-Shop-API
A Basic Shop API using NODEJS, EXPRESS, MONGODB, MONGOOSE

to sort, you must provide the query name "sort".
api/v1/product?sort=name

to sort in descending order, add - to the front of the property you want to sort
api/v1/product?sort=-name

to fetch a particular field name only, you must provide the query name "field"
api/v1/product?field=name,company